{
  "texts": [
    "The column NUMTOTV available in the dataset is used as labels to train a classifier in a supervised learning setting.",
    "Figure A1 in Appendix A shows the distribution of the number of vehicles.",
    "Most cases involve two vehicles, and only very few cases involve more than three vehicles.",
    "No cases involve zero vehicles.",
    "We could formulate the prediction problem as regression problem, with a suitable distributional assumption."
  ]
}